{"service_name": "Software Project Management", "service_id": "7920637924191128", "company_name": "BMT Defence Services Limited", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     BMT Defence Services Limited\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Software Project Management\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    BMT provide software project management services.  We use PRINCE2 project management methodologies by our certified practitioners, where applicable.  In addition, BMT are certified to ISO 9001:2008/27001.  We specialise in adopting agile and waterfall software methodologies on development projects - in addition to the management of helpdesk and support services.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     ISO 9001:2008/ISO27001:2013 accredited project management techniques\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Management of agile development projects\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Management reporting\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Project schedule creation and updating\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     PRINCE2 Project Management\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Management of multiple stakeholders\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Meeting/workshop organisation and facilitation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Identification of project risks and risk management\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Project financial progress reporting and performance\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Earned Value Management (EVM)\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Proven project performance from successful management of UK MOD projects\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Provision of single Point of Contact to simplify communication lines\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Proven project delivery experience from large-scale MOD projects\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Accurate reviews of project status\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Regular progress review through face-to-face meetings\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Regular status updates /reviews\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Successful project delivery to time and budget\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3360.00 per unit per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92484/7920637924191128-pricing-document-2015-10-05-1135.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92484/7920637924191128-sfia-rate-card-2015-10-05-0651.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92484/7920637924191128-service-definition-document-2015-10-05-0726.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n   